de.unifrankfurt.informatik.dbis.dia.config

Class EntityConfigElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unifrankfurt.informatik.dbis.dia.config.EntityConfigElement

  • public class EntityConfigElement
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the configuration for a Variable.

    These are:

    • triple: The TripleTemplate (see also: TriplePattern)
    • type: The NodeType of the value
    • fieldName: The name of the Field annotated with the Variable. Is null if the Variable is non-mapped

    This class is immutable.
